Mail::AuthenticationResults::Header::Version(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation Mail::AuthenticationResults::Header::Version(3)

NAME

Mail::AuthenticationResults::Header::Version - Class modelling the AuthServID part of the Authentication Results Header

VERSION

version 1.20200824.1

DESCRIPTION

A version string, this may be associated with an AuthServID, Entry, Group, or SubEntry.

Please see Mail::AuthenticationResults::Header::Base
